<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Hi <%= @candidate.first_name %>,
    </p>

    <p>
      You now have an interview request! Interview requests are created by employers, recruiters, and other members of the CardinalTalent platform. Go to your <%= link_to "Dashboard", new_user_session_url %> to review your interview requests.
    </p>

    <p>
      This opportunity comes from an employer interested in your profile.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you accept an interview request from <%= @user.first_name %>&nbsp;<%= @user.last_name %>, a CardinalTalent Account Manager will be in contact with you about the details of your candidacy.
    </p>

    <p>
      In a hurry to get started? Contact your CardinalTalent Account Manager directly via email. <%= mail_to "alex@cardinalhire.com" %>
    </p>

    <p>
      For more information and to opt-out or manage your subscriptions, visit our <%= link_to 'website', 'https://www.cardinalhire.com' %> or contact us.
    </p>

    <p>
      Contact Team<br />
      CardinalTalent.com
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
